scene.message:
Nanjo: Kido... Reiji Kido,{nl}
was it...{waitkey}{nl}
He seems unremarkable at a{nl}
glance, but I suspect he{nl}
does it on purpose.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That girl's a Reiji{nl}
fan, apparently...{waitkey}{clearbox}N-not that I'm jealous{nl}
or anything!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: No time to waste on{nl}
this dumb chatter!{nl}
Let's hurry to the hospital.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Senpai, "Kido" is in{nl}
your class, right?{waitkey}I never catch him in the room{nl}
at break or after school. I{nl}
want to talk to him, but I{nl}
never get the chance!{waitkey}That mysterious profile is{nl}
just so dreamy!{wait_fr:48}{nl}
...is what I mean...{waitkey}{ret}
